---
description: Project-wide context for the handcrafts e-commerce site
alwaysApply: true
---
- Project: E-commerce site for a local handcrafts/mugs/hats business.
- Stack: Next.js (App Router), Supabase (Postgres + Auth + Storage), Tailwind CSS, Resend (email), deployed on Vercel.
- Payment: COD only — no payment gateway. Do not suggest Stripe/PayPal integration.
- Guest checkout is allowed (cart via localStorage). Wishlist is account-only.
- Roles: customer, staff, admin — enforced via Supabase RLS, not just frontend checks.
- Keep components small and typed (TypeScript). No `any` unless unavoidable.
- Before writing DB-touching code, check schema in /docs/schema.sql if present.
